{"tid":1900385,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"惠譽： 香港中期財政轉弱但不影響評級","createTime":"2020-02-27T07:49:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T07:49:19.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4844ce90fb4781eadc85b07c8a60245ba97ba311","tid":1900385,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:49:19.000Z","msg":"惠譽：香港中期財政狀況不影響評級<br />\n<br />\n評級機構惠譽說，香港財政預算案提出的中期評估，顯示香港中期財政狀況會轉弱，但由於仍有龐大財政儲備，不會對評級構成壓力，維持香港「AA」評級，前景仍然是「負面」，主要考慮到社會持續不穩，經濟繼續受壓，損害香港的營商環境吸引力，亦會損害有效管治的形象。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1269338&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1269338%26csid%3D261_341&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgZFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=80acf47e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1269338&amp;csid=261_341</a>"}]}